      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> general of Kazavon's armies, executed minutes before the Star Tower fell — risen as a juju zombie in the War Room (E11) beside the @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-hazards.Actor.curseOfTheWorm01]{Curse of the Worm} haunt. The sayona <strong>Risibeth</strong> (E7 — his old war-commander, run as an Elite @UUID[Compendium.cotct-pf2e-conversion.cotct-actors.Actor.aerilayaBanshe01]{Aerilaya}-style spirit) trades castle-intelligence for a disturbing taste of living blood: she names three anchors and points to the chapel for the fourth.</p>",
